This rule specifies the packages in this monorepo and you should use them.

Each folder in ROOT_DIR/app or ROOT_DIR/lib is a package.

- `/app/blog` The main package, a astro project of my blog
- `/app/api` the backend of my blog, serving api endpoints in the `/api` path of url.
- `/lib/markdown` All things related to transform markdown to html or hast.
- `/lib/api-datatypes` stores the zod schemas for api, used in both blog and api package. Complicated types should go into this project.